    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>Marmite</strong> and 80ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[100ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[160ml] </span><strong>very cold water </strong>in a bowl,<strong> </strong>stirring continuously until fully combined – this is your <strong>Marmite water</strong></p><p>Add 60g <span class=\"text-purple\">[90g] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[120g]</span> <strong>flour</strong> to a separate large bowl with <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>(save the rest for later!), a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and the<strong> Marmite water</strong></p><p>Stir everything together thoroughly until there are no lumps, then set aside for later – this is your <strong>batter</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
