    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>sea bass fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper and cut each fillet in half on a diagonal</p><p>Season the<strong> sea bass</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and sprinkle both sides with <strong>flour</strong> until fully coated, then tap off any excess</p>",
      "order": 4,
